Package: supplysidemonitor
Type: Package
Title: Create Supply Side Monitor
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Leo", "MÃ¼hlenweg",, "leonard.muehlenweg@dezernatzukunft.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package is a wrapper for the functions used to create the interactive Supply Side Monitor created by Dezernat Zukunft e.V.    It automatically loads data from destatis and macrobond (authentification needed!) and creates an interactive reactable monitoring prices, output volume, and limiting factors.    A detailed description of the method can be found somewhere.
